reviews.text: What can I say.... The staff were borderline rude... As if we owe them lots of money... Why? I dunno.... Somehow.... Our happy hour didn't turn out that happy after all.... Definitely need to help them be a bit happier....
cozy and chilling with awesome blue lights and clouds indoor. We came at happy hour beterr 22.30 and 23.30. Good place.

There’s a variety of drinks available here and it is a good bar to hangout in if you’re in the Mongkok area. We went there as a group post work on a weekday. The ambience is wonderfully curated and they’ve got a good variety of drinks and food. 

I had the Lychee Martini and it was pretty darn good.

Sky  Bar and the restaurant next to,  they used to have free service charge zone but it was no longer exist. What is more,  the service at Sky Bar was horriblehorriblehorriblehorrible. 

The worst experience was at Sky BarBar ! We visited there very often.  It's almost Easter so we bought a small chocolate egg up there to celebrate the seasons.   A thin waitet apprached us immediately once I unwrapped the small chocolate egg and warned us don't eat anything out of the menu!  I replied him that it only a small chocolate egg then he said" you can't anyway! " After that , he kept standing behind me and stared at us ! What the hell Sky Bar?! 

Such a poor attitude and impolite tone were totally out of basic service standard ! No wonder the restaurant was so quiet even they are offering $128 (2 hours happy hours)! 

It was disappointed , we definitely won't visit Sky Bar,  Langham Place again!
Good seafood place

reviews.text: 每次泥味道都5太同😂食物目前龍蝦湯推薦。

西班牙黑豚風腿蜜瓜柚子沙律 $158
好多蜜瓜呀！！🧡夠鮮甜！配Parma ham真係一流👍🏻
.
Oyster Platter $298/6pcs
生蠔好鮮甜、creamy、有啲嘅海水味特別濃郁！
.
精選凍海鮮盤 $388
咩都有啲，岩晒鍾意食凍海鮮嘅朋友！生蠔大大隻！😍冰鮑魚同長腳蟹都好鮮甜！🤤👍🏻
.
香蒜汁烤日本一口牛 $138
超香呀！🤤好大碟！好惹味！😍一口牛好入味，不過如果腍啲會更好☺️
.
澳洲穀飼200日肉眼扒配巴黎牛油 $288
牛扒超大塊！！牛味濃、juicy！🤤薯菜嘅賣相幾得意🤣
.
巨峰提子特飲 $78
幾得意！提子波波冰好正！放好耐都唔會淡啦🤣好飲！💜

一個要工作的星期六，窩夫與蝦子餅放工後去旺角The Sky Bar吃晚飯。

選擇The Sky Bar是因為蝦子餅要觀看熱刺對阿仙奴的球賽。

第一道主菜是爐烤胡椒美國極黑豚扒伴菠蘿($278)，賣相很吸引。最上層的新鮮菠蘿片帶點酸，十分開胃，菠蘿加胡椒的味道出奇地夾。美國極黑豚扒加了大量胡椒來烤，胡椒味非常香濃，有少許辣。美國極黑豚扒十分厚身，烤完後肉汁還得以保留，只是稍嫌胡椒的味道蓋過了黑豚的肉香。

第二道主菜是黑松露醬焗幼嫩羊架伴番茄芝士焗蠔($288)，賣相同樣精美。先品嚐番茄芝士焗蠔，生蠔很新鮮，夠大隻，焗得剛剛好，不會過熟過乾。切開羊架，羊肉顏色粉嫩，肉質也很嫩，五成熟控制得宜，不過黑松露醬的味道並不明顯。墊底的黑松露薯蓉很幼滑，大大粒的橙色番茄十分香甜。

What can I say.... The staff were borderline rude... As if we owe them lots of money... Why? I dunno.... Somehow.... Our happy hour didn't turn out that happy after all.... Definitely need to help them be a bit happier....
cozy and chilling with awesome blue lights and clouds indoor. We came at happy hour beterr 22.30 and 23.30. Good place.
